.DT
components
Discworld command help
components

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
components - List the components required to cast a spell
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
components [for] <spell>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command will list those components (not targets) required to begin casting a spell.  You must know the spell in question in order to find out this information.  

Note that some spells have side effects in addition to merely consuming components; see the help files for each particular spell for more information.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> components for Hag's Blessing
You don't need anything to cast Hag's Blessing

> components Pragi's Fiery Gaze
Pragi's Fiery Gaze will consume an eye.

> components Mama Blackwing's Potent Preserver
Mama Blackwing's Potent Preserver requires a frog and a lit candle but
will not consume them.
.EI

.SH See also:
.SI 5
spells
.EI
